<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-03-26T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-03-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="421" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d421">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Señor <persName type="from">Romero</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Mexico</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-03-26"><hi rend="italic">March 26,
                                1896</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Mr. secretary</hi>: Since I sent you my note of the
                            18th instant, relative to the extradition of Inez Ruiz, Jesus Guerra,
                            and Juan Duque, I have learned that the decisions of the Supreme Court
                            of Justice of the United States do not take effect until thirty days
                            from the date of their promulgation have elapsed, and I therefore
                            consider that it will not be possible to effect the extradition of those
                            persons, in virtue of the decision of the Supreme Court of the 16th
                            instant, until the said period has expired.</p>
                        <p>I consequently postpone until that time the request contained in my
                            aforesaid note.</p>
                        <p>Accept, etc.,</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">M. Romero.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>